title: Day 3: Fast Food with Kaillie Humphreys
description:
American bobsledder Kaillie Humphreys may be a newly-minted American citizen, but she is on her fourth  Winter Olympic games. She joins In the Village to give insight into the fast food and fast tracks in Beijing.

Follow In The Village an Amazon Music for an inside look at the athlete life in Beijing, and watch all the Olympic action unfold on the networks of NBC
author: tess.quinlan@nbcuni.com (NBC Olympics)
